//check terminated_NF_imply_delete_request  for 3 but exactly 1 oCloud, exactly 1 NF, exactly 2 Request, exactly 1 Node, 20 steps
//check terminated_NF_cannot_be_redeployed for 3 but exactly 1 oCloud, exactly 1 NF, exactly 2 Request, exactly 1 Node, 20 steps
check termination_implies_resource_deallocation for 3 but exactly 1 oCloud, exactly 1 NF, exactly 2 Request, exactly 1 Node, 20 steps
check requests_end_in_response for 3 but exactly 1 oCloud, exactly 1 NF, exactly 2 Request, exactly 1 Node, 20 steps

run {} for 3 but exactly 1 oCloud, exactly 1 NF, exactly 2 Request, exactly 1 Node



